However, Mr Lowe says when he went to check if his show had been approved two days prior to broadcast, it had not been listened to.

He told the newspaper: 'I immediately emailed the managing editor and said "I see it has not been approved, we are getting a bit close for comfort."

'He immediately came back to me and said "Ok, I will deal with that". I said "Thanks a lot" and forgot about it.

